::Kaiser::
       He hops to his feet and backs away from DeathSteel.  He twirls his 
scimitars and then sheaths them on his hips.  "As I said before.  Adequate.  
Now go tend to your wounds, you will be needed soon."  He walks over to 
Tyrael and motions for him to join him off to the side for a private 
conversation after DeathSteel leaves.

--part1_3f.1a767b3b.2bb6fd8b_boundary
